POST-INSTALL:

		* Add the line below to your X11 configuration file:
		FontPath     "/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/fonts/misc"
				

		* Type the following commands:
		# cd /usr/X11R6/lib/X11/fonts/misc

		# ttmkfdir > fonts.dir 
		or
		# mkfontdir .

                and then:
                # chkfontpath --add /usr/X11R6/lib/X11/fonts/misc
                # xset fp rehash

TEST:

		* To test the font :
	       xlsfonts | grep orly


